loki.Title: Loki
loki.Actors: Tom Hiddleston, Owen Wilson, Sophia Di Martino
loki.Plot: The mercurial villain Loki resumes his role as the God of Mischief in a new series that takes place after the events of “Avengers: Endgame.”
loki.Awards: Nominated for 6 Primetime Emmys. 12 wins & 53 nominations total
